| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5901 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1ca3755e-f1f9-5cc5-8e5c-0af191c44951"
